**How to use Claude as a personal trainer**

1/ Body Assessment

Paste to Claude: "Here are my stats: [weight] lbs, [height], [age], [M/F]. Goal: [lose fat/build muscle/both]. I have access to [no equipment/ dumbbells/full gym]. Act as my personal trainer and nutritionist. Build me a realistic 12-week plan." 

2/ Meal Plan

Paste to Claude: "Build me a 7-day meal plan. [calorie target] calories/day, [protein target]g+ protein, low processed carbs. Keep it cheap and easy to prep. I don't eat [restrictions]. Include macros for every meal and a full grocery list I can get at Walmart or Costco." 

3/ Workout Program

Paste to Claude: "Create a [3/4/5]-day workout plan for [fat loss/muscle gain/both]. I train at [home with no equipment/home with dumbbells/a full gym]. Each session [minutes] minutes. My level: [beginner/intermediate/advanced]. Make it progressively harder over 12 weeks." 

4/ Craving Killer

Paste to Claude: "Give me 10 high-volume snacks under 150 calories that kill sugar cravings. Only stuff I can find at any grocery store. Also give me a short phrase I can repeat when I want to hit a drive-through at midnight." 

5/ Daily Check-In

Paste to Claude: "Act as my accountability coach. Give me 5 questions to answer every night: Did I follow my meal plan? Did I train? How many hours did I sleep? How much water? Rate my discipline 1-10. Format it as a daily tracker I can screenshot and fill in." 

6/ Plateau Breaker

Paste to Claude: "I've been stuck at [weight] lbs for [weeks]. Here's what I'm eating: [describe]. Here's my workout: [describe]. Tell me exactly what's wrong and what to change this week to start losing again."